title: Greg Casar
added: Casar often leads the charge on Austin City Council affordable housing projects. Despite his work establishing "affordable" projects for median income renters in other districts, his own district has accomplished the least amount of affordable housing projects in terms of the city's 10 year housing affordability plan. <ref>https://www.austinmonitor.com/stories/2021/10/city-failed-to-meet-its-affordable-housing-goals-in-2020/</ref>
